Seferino ABEITA et al. v. John LYNES. No. 4452. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. June 9, 1952. Tibo J. Chavez and Denis Cowper, Belen, N. Mex., for appellants. E. -C. Iden, Bryan G. Johnson and J. T. Paulantis, Albuquerque, N. Mex., for appel-lee.

Before PHILLIPS, Chief Judge, and BRATTON- and HUXMAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed June 9, 1952, pursuant to stipulation.
